			<div id=3D"iws_page_title_id" style=3D"text-align: center;">
				<h2 style=3D"text-align: left;">Crop Calculators
					<img alt=3D"" class=3D"alignright size-full wp-image-44203" src=3D"htt=
ps://www.ufseeds.com/on/demandware.static/-/Sites-UrbanFarmer-Library/defau=
lt/dw9a9cab6d/images/content/Screen-Shot-2017-10-06-at-10.36.47-AM.png">
				</h2>
			</div>
			<div style=3D"font-size: 12pt;">Interactive crop calculators for farmers=
 and gardeners. When growing vegetables in a garden or on a farm it=E2=80=
=99s always important to know how much seed is needed, when to plant, how m=
uch to plant and yield expectations. The calculators below will help with m=
any of these questions. Just click to download the calculator.</div>
