anFarmer-Library/default/dwbd4377ee/images/content/When_to_Plant_Spring_Veg=
etable_Seeds_Calculator.xlsx" rel=3D"noopener" style=3D"font-size: 12pt; fo=
nt-weight: bold;" target=3D"_blank" title=3D"When to Plant Spring Vegetable=
 Seeds Calculator">Spring Vegetable Schedule Calculator</a>

			</div>
